      </paragraph>
      <paragraph>
        <num>82.</num>
        <content>
          <p>The net benefits to individuals are estimated by calculating the total payments from maternity pay (SMP and MA) less maternity allowance prior to policy implementation, aggregated across all the women who would be protected from redundancy while pregnant. We <b><i>estimate an annual benefit of £2.9m per year to individuals from maternity payments less maternity allowance</i></b>.</p>
        </content>
