        <num>139.</num>
        <content>
          <p>We calculate the weighted median wage for three broad age bands, as data on mother’s age at birth is separated according to these age bands. ASHE data on median weekly pay and number of employees is used for these calculations. This approach is set out in the box below for females aged 16–29 as an example. </p>
